GOALS
Get CSS formatting to where I am satisfied with it
Add a dollar sign before monthly costs and annual salaries
Add commas if monthly costs or annual salaries are greater than 1,000 (or 1,000,000)
display decimals monthly costs and annuals salaries to the hundredth
    OR remove any decimals
Add the ability to accept various formats for the annual salary input
    plain number - 1000
    leading dollar sign - $1000
    commas - 1,000
    decimals - 1000.01

CSS Combinators
(space) descendant selector
    Targets all descendants of a specified type
> child selector
    Targets all children of the specified type
+ adjacent sibling selector
    Targets the immediate following sibling of the specified type
~ general sibling selector
    Targets all subsequent siblings of the specified type